class="hl-label blue">中道崩殂</mark> 。今天下三分，<mark class="hl-label pink">益州疲敝</mark> ，此诚<mark class="hl-label red">危急存亡之秋</mark> 也！然侍衞之臣，不懈于内；<mark class="hl-label purple">忠志之士</mark> ，忘身于外者，盖追先帝之殊遇，欲报之于陛下也。诚宜开张圣听，以光先帝遗德，恢弘志士之气；不宜妄自菲薄，引喻失义，以塞忠谏之路也。<br>宫中、府中，俱为一体；陟罚臧否，不宜异同。若有<mark class="hl-label orange">作奸</mark> 、<mark class="hl-label green">犯科</mark> ，及为忠善者，宜付有司，论其刑赏，以昭陛下平明之治；不宜偏私，使内外异法也。</p><h1 id="timeline"><a href="#timeline" class="headerlink" title="timeline"></a>timeline</h1><div class="timeline undefined"><div class='timeline-item headline'><div class='timeline-item-title'><div class='item-circle'><p>2022</p></div></div></div><div class='timeline-item'><div class='timeline-item-title'><div class='item-circle'><p>04-02</p></div></div><div class='timeline-item-content'><p>这是测试页面</p></div></div></div><p>red,pink,purple,blue,orange,green</p><div class="timeline purple"><div class='timeline-item headline'><div class='timeline-item-title'><div class='item-circle'><p>2022</p></div></div></div><div class='timeline-item'><div class='timeline-item-title'><div class='item-circle'><p>01-02</p></div></div><div class='timeline-item-content'><p>这是测试页面</p></div></div></div><h1 id="flink"><a href="#flink" class="headerlink" title="flink"></a>flink</h1><div class="flink"><div class="flink-name">友情链接</div><div class="flink-desc">那些人，那些事</div> <div class="flink-list">          <div class="flink-list-item">            <a href="https://jerryc.me/" title="Frank" target="_blank">              <div class="flink-item-icon">                <img class="no-lightbox" src="https://jerryc.me/img/avatar.png" onerror='this.onerror=null;this.src="/gitee-blog/img/friend_404.gif"' alt="Frank" />              </div>              <div class="flink-item-name">Frank</div>               <div class="flink-item-desc" title="今日事,今日毕">今日事,今日毕</div>            </a>          </div>          <div class="flink-list-item">            <a href="https://hexo.io/zh-tw/" title="Hexo" target="_blank">              <d